  <brief_title>The Objective is to Respond to Patients' Needs in the Field of Larynx Replacement</brief_title>
  <official_title>Artificial Larynx : Intralaryngeal Prosthesis With Valve in Major Swallowing Troubles</official_title>
  <sponsors>
