    <intervention_name>Implantation of intralaryngeal prosthesis with a new double valve system, allowing tracheotomy closing</intervention_name>
    <description>An artificial Larynx composed of a tracheobronxane ® Dumon ST prosthesis and a valves system will be implant under general anesthesia by endoscopy. The 3 first patients will be patients with tracheotomy, in order to allow breathing through this tracheotomy in case of valves dysfunction.</description>
